{"tid":1374024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"防暴警挑機「冇證」外籍兼職記者 自揭英文差終笠水","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T02:06:31.000Z","uid":111253,"like":553,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"b6be3c5cdab9cf0b25328ebdb810887b8aacbc63","tid":1374024,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:59:33.000Z","msg":"我睇左D乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190728/59870764?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3GoN64u08JCDn_xvn9HRJbyJnMCgXhyFaotDzXKYlk6Te2PzbONCWNhwc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190728%2F59870764%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3GoN64u08JCDn_xvn9HRJbyJnMCgXhyFaotDzXKYlk6Te2PzbONCWNhwc&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F15zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=1ec2c572\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190728%2F59870764%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3GoN64u08JCDn_xvn9HRJbyJnMCgXhyFaotDzXKYlk6Te2PzbONCWNhwc&h=c64be7a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190728/59870764?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3GoN64u08JCDn_xvn9HRJbyJnMCgXhyFaotDzXKYlk6Te2PzbONCWNhwc</a><br />\n<br />\n香港警察近年被戲稱「毅進仔」，除其邏輯思辨能力被質疑，就連中英文都要惡補。繼4個警察協會昨日去信特首林鄭月娥，錯寫上款「林太」為「林女士」而鬧笑話後，昨晚（27日）光復元朗現場有防暴警質疑外籍兼職記者沒有記者證時，自曝其英語聆聽能力低下，《蘋果》粗略整理二人對話：<br />\n防暴警：What's your press? What's your company?（你屬於哪間傳媒？）<br />\n外籍記者：I work as freelance.（我是兼職記者。）<br />\n防暴警：Freelance, so no company.（兼職，所以不屬於任何傳媒。）<br />\n外籍記者：Freelance.（兼職。）<br />\n防暴警：Freelance press.（兼職記者。）<br />\n外籍記者：From University of Hong Kong.（來自香港大學。）<br />\n防暴警：What's your use, the photo?（拍下的相有何用？）<br />\n外籍記者：Just self（只是自用。）<br />\n防暴警：Yourself.（你自用。）<br />\n外籍記者：Yea.（對。）<br />\n防暴警：Send to where?（傳送到哪處？）<br />\n外籍記者：It's up to me, as my business.（這是我的事業，由我決定。）<br />\n防暴警：It's your own. Right?（這是你的相片，對嗎？）<br />\n外籍記者：I am a freelancer, a freelance journalist. Is that a problem?（我做兼職，是兼職記者，有問題嗎？）<br />\n防暴警：Freelance journalist. OK.（兼職記者，無問題。）<br />\n外籍記者：Yea.（對。）<br />\n防暴警：What's your name?（你叫甚麼名字？）<br />\n外籍記者：Brian. What's the problem?（我是Brian，有問題嗎？）<br />\n防暴警：Brian Problem.（你是Brian Problem。）<br />\n外籍記者：Brian. What's the problem?（我是Brian，有問題嗎？）<br />\n防暴警：Brian.（你是Brian。）<br />\n外籍記者：Yes.（對。）<br />\n防暴警：I have query. Why this is a...no...（我有問題，為何這個沒有...）<br />\n外籍記者：I am a freelancer...（我做兼職...）<br />\n防暴警：Emm...（哦...）<br />\n外籍記者：Yea.（對。）<br />\n防暴警：So What's your press ID?（那麼你的記者證呢？）<br />\n外籍記者：I am a freelance.（我是兼職記者。）<br />\n防暴警：Who know? No press ID either! Show your identity document!（誰知道？還要無記者證！出示你的身份證明文件！）<br />\n外籍記者：Yea I do have one.（咦我真是有證明。）<br />\n防暴警：Only the press ID!（只看記者證。）<br />\n（展示學生證）<br />\n外籍記者：I am a University of Hong Kong Master of Journalism student.（我是港大新聞碩士生。）<br />\n防暴警：Oh, you are a student!（噢，你是學生！）<br />\n外籍記者：Yes! Master of Journalism student. What are you going to do? I am Brian...（對！新聞碩士生，你要怎樣做？我是Brian...）<br />\n（向圍觀者展示證件）<br />\nI am Master of Journalism student of the University of Hong Kong. What are you questioning before?（我是港大新聞碩士生，你剛才質問甚麼？）<br />\n防暴警：Why don't you have a press ID?（為何你沒有記者證？）<br />\n外籍記者：Because I'm a student!（因為我是學生！）<br />\n防暴警：I know, I know.（我知，我知。）<br />\n外籍記者：OK, so what's the problem?（那麼還有甚麼問題？）<br />\n防暴警：Be careful.（請你小心。）<br />\n外籍記者：I'm trying to be careful, thank you.（我會盡量小心，多謝你。）"},{"pid":"4f6d5e7044b22b3ba448639397683b5af9574ae9","tid":1374024,"uid":111253,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e225546d8f1316b9dac16c1ba70ac0e9afe6d6f","tid":1374024,"uid":249187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29eadf9d020892cbcb99dca66c98c986acf3d336","tid":1374024,"uid":256939,"like":108,"dislike":0,"score":108,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:04:34.000Z","msg":"Ok 下次學佢 講 I am Brain 睇下佢會唔會放我走"},{"pid":"6d6a3a826e70316f45b086faf55636bdee79c4e1","tid":1374024,"uid":256939,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"29eadf9d020892cbcb99dca66c98c986acf3d336","tid":1374024,"uid":256939,"like":108,"dislike":0,"score":108,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:04:34.000Z","msg":"Ok 下次學佢 講 I am Brain 睇下佢會唔會放我走"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:05:17.000Z","msg":"Brian"},{"pid":"37f79d87783a1c1b565709599f45ca9c202efb89","tid":1374024,"uid":75767,"like":120,"dislike":0,"score":120,"quote":{"pid":"6d6a3a826e70316f45b086faf55636bdee79c4e1","tid":1374024,"uid":256939,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"29eadf9d020892cbcb99dca66c98c986acf3d336","tid":1374024,"uid":256939,"like":108,"dislike":0,"score":108,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:04:34.000Z","msg":"Ok 下次學佢 講 I am Brain 睇下佢會唔會放我走"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:05:17.000Z","msg":"Brian"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:06:26.000Z","msg":"Brian problem"},{"pid":"67